# Supplier & Third-Party Cybersecurity Due Diligence – Audit Checklist

## 1. Defined Due Diligence Process
- [ ] Does the organization have a defined process for conducting due diligence on potential suppliers and other third-party service providers before entering into a formal relationship?

**Audit Evidence / Prüfpunkte:**
- Dokumentierter Due-Diligence-Prozess
- Genehmigung durch Management / Procurement / CISO
- Historie der Überprüfungen
- Integration in Governance- oder ERM-Richtlinien

---

## 2. Cybersecurity Assessments & Checks
- [ ] What types of cybersecurity-related assessments and checks are performed as part of the due diligence process (e.g., security controls, risk assessments, incident history)?

**Audit Evidence / Prüfpunkte:**
- Checklisten oder Assessment-Templates
- Nachweis durch Reports oder Bewertungsdokumente
- Einbeziehung von Security Controls, Risikoanalysen, Incident History
- Referenzen auf Standards (z. B. ISO 27001, NIST)

---

## 3. Evaluation of Potential Cybersecurity Risks
- [ ] How does the organization evaluate the potential cybersecurity risks associated with a supplier or third-party before onboarding them?

**Audit Evidence / Prüfpunkte:**
- Dokumentierte Risiko-Bewertungsmethodik
- Risiko-Klassifizierung (High/Medium/Low) und Priorisierung
- Integration in Risk Registers oder Supplier-Risk-Dashboards
- Nachweis der Management-Entscheidungen basierend auf Bewertung

---

## 4. Criteria & Thresholds for Acceptability
- [ ] Are there clear criteria and thresholds established for determining the acceptability of cybersecurity risks posed by potential suppliers and third parties?

**Audit Evidence / Prüfpunkte:**
- Definition von Risiko-Schwellenwerten dokumentiert
- Entscheidungsmatrix oder Bewertungsrichtlinien
- Nachweis der Anwendung bei Onboarding-Entscheidungen
- Management-Freigaben bei Überschreitung von Toleranzen

---

## 5. Financial & Business Continuity Assessment
- [ ] Does the organization's due diligence process include an assessment of the supplier's or third-party's financial stability, ownership structure, and overall business continuity capabilities?

**Audit Evidence / Prüfpunkte:**
- Finanzberichte, Ownership-Dokumentation oder Ratings
- Business Continuity / Disaster Recovery Assessment
- Integration in Due-Diligence-Reports
- Nachweis der Verwendung in Onboarding-Entscheidungen

---

## 6. Documentation & Communication of Results
- [ ] How does the organization document and communicate the results of the due diligence process to the relevant stakeholders involved in the supplier or third-party selection decision?

**Audit Evidence / Prüfpunkte:**
- Due-Diligence-Reports dokumentiert
- Verteilung an relevante Stakeholder (Procurement, Security, Management)
- Nachweis der Kenntnisnahme und Genehmigung
- Protokolle oder Entscheidungsmemos
